                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="footer__line footer__line--bottom" />
        </div>
        <div class="footer__section footer__section--middle">
            <h3 class="footer__section_title">Páginas</h3>
            <nav class="footer__nav">
                <ul class="footer__nav_content">
                    <li class="footer__nav_link">
                        <a class="link-animation" href="/">Início</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="footer__nav_link">
                        <a class="link-animation" href="/empresa">Empresa</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="footer__nav_link">
                        <a class="link-animation" href="/servicos">Serviços</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="footer__nav_link">
                        <a class="link-animation" href="/portfolio">Portfolio</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="footer__nav_link">
                        <a class="link-animation" href="/orcamento">Orçamento</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="footer__nav_link">
                        <a class="link-animation" href="/contactos">Contactos</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
            <div class="footer__policies">
                <small class="footer__usage_terms">
                    <a href="/">Termos de uso</a>
                </small>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="5" width="5" viewBox="0 0 512 512"><!--!Font Awesome Free 6.7.2 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free Copyright 2024 Fonticons, Inc.--><path fill="#9e9e9e" d="M256 512A256 256 0 1 0 256 0a256 256 0 1 0 0 512z"/></svg>
                <small class="footer__privacy_policy">
                    <a href="/">Política de privacidade</a>
                </small>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer__divider">
            <div class="footer__line footer__line--full" />
        </div>
        <div class="footer__section footer__section--right">
            <h3 class="footer__section_title">Pedido de Orçamento</h3>
            <p>Envie-nos uma proposta de orçamento sem compromisso! Resposta em menos de 48 horas.</p>
            <form class="footer__form">
                <input 
                    class="footer__input"  
                    type="email"
                    name="email"
                    placeholder="Insira o seu email"
                    maxlength="60" 
                />
                <input
                    class="footer__form_submit button--primary"
                    type="submit"
                    value="Enviar"
                 />
            </form>
            <small class="footer__author">
                Desenvolvido por David Delgado em Astro
            </small>
        </div>
        <small class="footer__copyright">
            &copy; 2024 www.mysite.com - All Rights Reserved.
        </small>
    </div>
</footer>

<style>
    .footer {
        position: relative;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 500px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        background: var(--blue-primary);
        background: -moz-linear-gradient(102deg, var(--blue-primary) 0%, rgba(0,29,61,1) 100%);
        background: -webkit-linear-gradient(102deg, var(--blue-primary) 0%, rgba(0,29,61,1) 100%);
        background: linear-gradient(102deg, var(--blue-primary) 0%, rgba(0,29,61,1) 100%);
        color: var(--gray-background);
    }
    .footer__content {
        --max-width: var(--header-width);
        --min-margin: 50px;
        max-width: calc(var(--max-width) + 2*var(--min-margin));
        width: 100%;
        height: 300px;
        display: flex;
        padding: 0 var(--min-margin);
    }
    .footer__section--left, .footer__section--right {
        flex-basis: 420px;
    }
    .footer__section--left {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding-right: 60px;
    }
    .footer__section--middle {
        flex-basis: 560px;
        padding: 0 8%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }
    .footer__section--right {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        padding-left: 60px;
    }
    .footer__section--right .footer__section_title {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .footer__section--right p {
        font: var(--text-base);
        color: var(--gray-background);
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .footer__section_title {
        font: var(--h4);
        font-weight: 400;
        color: var(--blue-secondary);
    }
    .footer__nav {
        flex: 1;
        margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .footer__nav_content {
        list-style-type: none;
        padding: 0;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
        grid-template-rows: repeat(3, 1fr);
        column-gap: 25px;
    }
    .footer__nav_link {
        padding: 18px 0;
    }
    .footer__nav_link > a {
        color: var(--gray-background);
        font: var(--text-xl);
        position: relative;
    }
    .footer__divider {
        position: relative;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-rows: 1fr auto 1fr;
        justify-items: center;
        height: 100%;
    }
    .footer__line {
        border-right: 2px solid var(--gray-background);
    }
    .footer__line--full {
        grid-row: 1 / 4;
    }
    .footer__line--top {
        grid-row: 1;
    }
    .footer__line--bottom {
        grid-row: 3;
    }
    .footer__divider.footer__divider--contacts .footer__contacts {
        grid-row: 2;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-rows: repeat(3, 1fr);
        padding: 10px 0;
    }
    .footer__divider.footer__divider--contacts .footer__contacts > a {
        padding: 2px;
        color: var(--gray-background);
        height: 32px;
        box-sizing: content-box;
    }
    .footer__copyright {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .footer__slogan {
        display: flex;
        height: 50px;
        gap: 20px;
    }
    .footer__slogan :not(img) {
        flex: 1;
        font: var(--text-xl);
        color: white;
    }
    .footer__slogan img {
        color: var(--blu-secondary);
        flex: 0;
    }
    .footer__contact {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 15px;
    }
    .footer__contact:first-child {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .footer__policies {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .footer__policies > *:not(:last-child) {
        margin-right: 20px;
        display: inline-block;
    }
    .footer__policies a {
        color: var(--gray-500);
    }
    .footer__form {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .footer__input {
        padding: 8px 10px;
        max-width: 300px;
        width: 100%;
        font: var(--text-sm);
        color: var(--gray-900);
        border-radius: 5px;
        border: 1px solid black;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .footer__form_submit {
        width: 100px;
        height: 40px;
    }
    .footer__author {
        margin-top: auto;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
        color: var(--gray-500);
    }


    @media only screen and (max-width: 1200px) {
        .footer {
            height: unset;
        }
        .footer__content {
            height: auto;
            margin: 100px 0;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
            grid-template-rows: auto auto;
            grid-template-areas: 
                "left ver middle"
                "hor hor hor"
                "right right right";
        }
        .footer__section--left {
            grid-area: left;
        }
        .footer__section--middle {
            grid-area: middle;
            padding: 0 18%;
        }
        .footer__section--right {
            grid-area: right;
            padding-left: 0;
        }
        .footer__divider:not(.footer__divider--contacts) {
            grid-area: hor;
            padding: 60px 0;
        }
        .footer__line--full {
            border: none;
            border-top: 2px solid var(--gray-background);
            width: 100%;
        }
        .footer__form {
            flex-direction: row;
        }
        .footer__input {
            margin-right: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
    }


    @media only screen and (max-width: 768px) {
        .footer__content {
            grid-template-columns: auto;
            grid-template-rows: auto auto auto auto auto;
            grid-template-areas: 
                "left"
                "hor1"
                "middle"
                "hor2"
                "right";
        }
        .footer__logo, .footer__slogan {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer__section--middle {
            padding: 0;
        }
        .footer__nav_content {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer__policies {
            justify-content: flex-start;
        }
        .footer__divider--contacts {
            grid-area: hor1;
            padding: 60px 0;
            grid-template-rows: 0 auto 0;
        }
        .footer__divider:not(.footer__divider--contacts) {
            grid-template-columns: auto;
            grid-area: hor2;
            padding: 60px 0;
        }
        .footer__line--top, .footer__line--bottom {
            border: none;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gray-background);
            width: 100%;
            height: 18px;
        }
        .footer__divider {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
        }
        .footer__divider.footer__divider--contacts .footer__contacts {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            grid-template-rows: auto;
            grid-column: 2;
            padding: 0 10px;
        }
        .footer__line--top {
            grid-column: 1;
            grid-row: 1;
        }
        .footer__line--bottom {
            grid-column: 3;
            grid-row: 1;
        }
    }

</style>